      <h2 class="cfg-modal-title">Delete Label</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="cfg-modal-body">Are you sure you want to delete <strong id="cfg-del-label-name-txt"></strong>? It will be removed from all APIs using it. This action can't be undone.</p>
